data.description: RARE FIND: SINGLE LEVEL LIVING!!! Enjoy everything that is offered within this one-owner home which has been meticulously maintained and thoughtfully designed for your comfort and convenience. Embrace the potential to double your square footage by finishing the basement, offering endless possibilities for customization.  Step outside onto one of two large decks, perfect for relaxing and taking in beautiful sunsets overlooking the fully fenced-in back yard. The open kitchen and living room boast cathedral ceilings, creating a spacious and inviting atmosphere. The main living areas feature new luxury vinyl plank flooring for a modern and elegant touch. New refrigerator. New microwave.  The home includes three bedrooms and an office, providing plenty of space for daily living and work-from-home needs. Cozy up on cool nights by the wood-burning fireplace, adding warmth and charm to the living room.  This home is a rare find, offering comfort, potential, and style in one package. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!
